        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl0_Label1"><p>Iperius is a lightweight, powerful and flexible Hyper-V backup software. In fact, it can perform backups of Microsoft Hyper-V virtual machines (also in incremental and differential RCT mode) and on multiple destinations, such as Tape LTO or NAS, Cloud or FTP, and without limitations in the number of virtual machines or in the size of [&hellip;]</p>
